How GitHub Enterprise works Learn how GitHub Enterprise works

Access controlled

Encourage teams to work together while limiting access to those who need it with granular permissions and authentication through SAML/SSO and LDAP.

Hosted where you need itSecurely and reliably host your work on GitHub using GitHub Enterprise Cloud. Or deploy GitHub Enterprise Server in your own data centers or in a private cloud using Amazon Web Services, Azure, or Google Cloud Platform.
